title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
description: Description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains highlight and map rules, an exception is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
